MoreAngleView: You usually only get the first view.When you use this function.You can see the first view and the third ciew at the 
same time.(Mom no longer has to worry about me being shot as a hedgehog!)
更多视角：你一般只能看到第一视角，但是有了这个功能，你能同时看到第一视角和第三视角。(妈妈再也不用担心我被射成刺猬了！)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Elytra:At some server,you can't fly.When you use this function.You can fly with your elytra and fireworks rockets are higher.
(Careful landing too fierce)
鞘翅飞：在一些服务器里，你不能飞行。当你用了这个功能，你可以用鞘翅飞行，并用你的烟花火箭让你飞的更高。(小心摔死)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Search:Search some features.
搜索：搜索一些功能
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
GuiMove:When you open the GUI.You can move without closing the GUI.(It's a semi-finished product in Mod)
GUI移动：当你打开GUI时，你可以移动但不用关闭GUI。(Mod里那个是个半成品)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SafeWalk:When you walk to the edge of the block.You will sneak on the edge of the block.
(Don't jump out,you can landing too fierce!And use with Scaffold)
安全走路：当你走到方块边缘时，你会在方块边缘下蹲（别跳出去，会摔死的！配合自动搭路食用效果更佳！）
